==============================================================================
	SITE CONFIGURATION
==============================================================================
Edit the following for your site:

<supporttop>/config/RELEASE - Set EPICS_BASE to EPICS base pathname.
<supporttop>/xxx/configure/RELEASE - Set SUPPORT to <supporttop> pathname.
<supporttop>/utils/Makefile - Set SUPPORT to <supporttop> pathname.
			    - Add/delete support modules by adding/deleting
			    '#' to the four entries for each support module;
			 
			    include $(SUPPORT)/config/<module>_RELEASE
			    DIRS += $(module)
			    RELEASE_FILES += $(module)/configure/RELEASE
			    MASTER_FILES  += $(SUPPORT)/config/<module>_RELEASE

To rebuild synApps;

cd <supporttop>/utils
gnumake clean uninstall;gnumake

	
