MODULE:		mpfGpib
VERSION:	R1-4
URL: http://www.aps.anl.gov/asd/people/mrk/epics/modules/bus/gpib/mpfGpib/index.html
BUILD DEPENDENCIES: EPICS_BASE, MPF
PROCEDURE:
- After unzipping and untarring mpfGpib1-4.tar, "mv 1-4 mpfGpib1-4".
- cd <supporttop>; chmod u+w mpfGpib1-4/config/RELEASE
- Replace the contents of mpfGpib1-4/gpibApp/Makefile.Vx with the following;
------- Makefile.Vx -------
PROD      = GpibHideosLocal.o
PROD     += GpibHideosRemote.o

LIBOBJS   = GpibGsTi9914.o
LIBOBJS  += Gpib.o
LIBOBJS  += gpibSniff.o
LIBOBJS  += gpibServer.o
LIBNAME   = mpfgpibserverLib

INSTALLS  = GpibGsTi9914.o
INSTALLS += Gpib.o
INSTALLS += gpibSniff.o
INSTALLS += gpibServer.o
------- Makefile.Vx -------


MODULE:		motor
VERSION:	4-5
URL: http://www.aps.anl.gov/upd/people/sluiter/epics/motor/index.html
BUILD DEPENDENCIES: EPICS_BASE, MPF, MPF_GPIB
PROCEDURE:
- <top>/config/RELEASE. Uncomment MPF_SERIAL=, MPF=, EPICS_BASE=,
			TEMPLATE_TOP=, MSITOP= and MPF_GPIB=
			Delete all "include" lines.
- <top>/motorApp/Makefile.  All device support selected.
- <top>/motorExApp/Makefile.  Build all motor examples.


